20#include "config.h"
21#include "system.h"
22#include "coretypes.h"
23#include "tm.h"
24#include "opts.h"
25#include "signop.h"
26#include "hash-set.h"
27#include "selftest.h"
28
29#if CHECKING_P
30
31namespace selftest {
32
33/* Construct a hash_set <const char *> and verify that various operations
34 work correctly. */
35
36static void
37test_set_of_strings ()
38{
39 hash_set <const char *> s;
40 ASSERT_EQ (0, s.elements ());
41
42 const char *red = "red";
43 const char *green = "green";
44 const char *blue = "blue";
45
46 ASSERT_EQ (false, s.contains (red));
47
48 /* Populate the hash_set. */
49 ASSERT_EQ (false, s.add (red));
50 ASSERT_EQ (false, s.add (green));
51 ASSERT_EQ (false, s.add (blue));
52
53 /* Verify that the values are now within the set. */
54 ASSERT_EQ (true, s.contains (red));
55 ASSERT_EQ (true, s.contains (green));
56 ASSERT_EQ (true, s.contains (blue));
57}
58
59/* Run all of the selftests within this file. */
60
61void
62hash_set_tests_c_tests ()
63{
64 test_set_of_strings ();
65}
66
67} // namespace selftest
68
69#endif /* #if CHECKING_P */
